2015年8月21日，宣布《{{le|酒吧五傑|It’s Always Sunny In Philadelphia}}》副執行製作戴夫·徹寧（{{lang|en|Dave Chernin}}）與約翰·徹寧（{{lang|en|John Chernin}}）共同為[[福斯廣播公司|FOX]]開發新[[情景喜劇|情境喜劇]]，並由徹寧兄弟、{{le|3藝術娛樂|3 Arts Entertainment}}與[[二十世紀福斯電視公司|二十世紀福斯電視公司]]共同製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/fox-comedy-john-dave-chernin-1201503373/|title=Fox Nabs Comedy From John & Dave Chernin With Penalty|publisher=Deadline.com|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|date=2015-08-21|accessdate=2017-01-11|archive-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122230503/https://deadline.com/2015/08/fox-comedy-john-dave-chernin-1201503373/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年2月2日，FOX正式宣布預訂本劇試播集，而執導過《酒吧五傑》的{{le|藍道爾·艾因霍恩|Randall Einhorn}}將擔任試播集導演並身兼執行製作（僅試播集），徹寧兄弟和3藝術娛樂的奧利·奧布斯特（{{lang|en|Oly Obst}}）與尼克拉斯·弗蘭科（{{lang|en|Nicholas Frenkel}}）也將共同擔任執行製作。<ref name="Pilot">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/the-mick-comedy-pilot-john-dave-chernin-randall-einhorn-fox-1201694633/|title=Fox Orders Comedy Pilot From John & Dave Chernin, Randall Einhorn to Direct|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2016-05-19|date=2016-02-02|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130205729/https://deadline.com/2016/02/the-mick-comedy-pilot-john-dave-chernin-randall-einhorn-fox-1201694633/|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月10日，本劇正式獲FOX系列預訂，並作為[[2016年－2017年美國電視網節目表|2016年－2017年電視季度]]新劇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/the-exorcist-lethal-weapon-making-history-pitch-the-mick-apb-fox-series-orders-1201752948/|title='The Exorcist', 'Lethal Weapon', 'Making History', 'Pitch', 'The Mick' & 'APB' Get Fox Series Orders|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2016-05-11|date=2016-05-10|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|archive-date=2017-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802092034/http://deadline.com/2016/05/the-exorcist-lethal-weapon-making-history-pitch-the-mick-apb-fox-series-orders-1201752948/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月16日，由於艾因霍恩執導的《{{le|布偶總動員|The Muppets (TV series)}}》遭到[[美國廣播公司|ABC]]取消，故二十世紀福斯決定與其簽署合約，並讓艾因霍恩擔任本劇全季執行製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/randall-einhorn-deal-20th-tv-the-mick-executive-producer-1201774209/|title=Randall Einhorn Inks Deal With 20th TV, Joins ‘The Mick’ As Executive Producer|work=Deadline.com|first=Denise|last=Petski|accessdate=2017-01-11|date=2016-06-16|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108123150/https://deadline.com/2016/06/randall-einhorn-deal-20th-tv-the-mick-executive-producer-1201774209/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年1月11日，FOX於[[電視評論家協會|電視評論家協會]]上宣布追加第1季4集集數至17集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/the-mick-new-fox-comedy-four-additional-episodes-1201883224/|title=‘The Mick’: New Fox Comedy Gets Order For Four Additional Episodes – TCA|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2017-01-11|date=2017-01-11|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012947/https://deadline.com/2017/01/the-mick-new-fox-comedy-four-additional-episodes-1201883224/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月21日，FOX宣布續訂第2季。<ref name="Season 2 Renewed">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/comedy-the-mick-renewed-season-2-fox-kaitlin-olson-1201925383/|title=Kaitlin Olson Comedy ‘The Mick’ Renewed For Season 2 By Fox|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-02-21|accessdate=2017-02-21|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222070816/http://deadline.com/2017/02/comedy-the-mick-renewed-season-2-fox-kaitlin-olson-1201925383/|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月7日，FOX宣布追加預訂第2季7集集數至全季集數20集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2017/11/07/the-mick-full-season-2-episode-count-20-fox/|title=''The Mick'' Scores Full-ish Season 2 Order|work={{le|TVLine|TVLine}}|author=Michael Ausiello|date=2017-11-07|accessdate=2017-11-07|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107221701/http://tvline.com/2017/11/07/the-mick-full-season-2-episode-count-20-fox/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年5月10日，FOX宣布取消本劇。<ref name="Canceled">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-mick-canceled-by-fox-after-2-seasons-1202385687/|title=‘The Mick’ Canceled By Fox After 2 Seasons|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline.com|date=2018-05-10|accessdate=2018-05-10|archive-date=2018-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510223632/http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-mick-canceled-by-fox-after-2-seasons-1202385687/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

